text: Göran Daniel "Dani" Martinez Olsson (born 9 January 1973 in Stockholm) is a Swedish former footballer (midfielder). He played for Djurgårdens IF, Racing Club de Ferrol, Elche, Guadix, Universidad, Ceuta, Linense, and Puerto Real.http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.dani.olsson.96809.en.html He played 19 Allsvenskan matches for Djurgårdens IF. ==References== Category:Swedish footballers Category:Swedish expatriate footballers Category:Allsvenskan players Category:Segunda División B players Category:Djurgårdens IF Fotboll players Category:Racing de Ferrol footballers Category:Elche CF players Category:Universidad de Las Palmas CF footballers Category:AD Ceuta footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Spain Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Association football midfielders
